<topic xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="Internationalization-i18n">
  <title>Internationalization (i18n)</title>
  <body>
    <section id="section">
      <p>Serna <keyword>user interface</keyword><indexterm>user interface, localization</indexterm> is localized into a number of languages for the convenience of international users. The supported languages are:<ul>
          <li>
            <p>Chinese</p>
            <fig>
              <title>Chinese localization of Serna GUI.</title>
              <image href="chinese-gui.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
            </fig>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Dutch</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>English</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>French</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>German</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Igbo</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Italian</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Norwegian</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Russian</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Swedish</p>
          </li>
        </ul></p>
      <p>You can easily   <xref href="specifying-gui-language.xml">switch supported languages</xref>.</p>
    </section>
  </body>
